<th>维度</th>
<th>阳木（健康）</th>
<th>阴木（失衡）</th>
</tr></thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>身界</strong></td>
<td>挺拔如松</td>
<td>僵硬佝偻</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>心界</strong></td>
<td>正直担当</td>
<td>固执抗上</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>灵界</strong></td>
